Version 0.7.0
---------------------------
New features:
- Data exchange protocol is changed to JSON
- 'add-section' command

Version 0.6.1 (2015-12-14)
---------------------------
New features:
- /bin section (running commands)

Version 0.6.0 (2015-11-25)
---------------------------
New features:
- Directory-like tokens organisation structure
- Multiple datafiles storage
- --add-file command

Version 0.5.2 (2015-06-28)
---------------------------
New features:
- --auto-start option
- the issue with data file locking is fixed 

Version 0.5.1 (2015-06-26)
---------------------------
New features:
- Trusted IPs ('trusted_ips' regd.conf option).

Version 0.5.0 (2015-06-25)
---------------------------
New features:
- Access permissions on file socket servers.
- Statistics report (--report-stat command).
- Viewing log file (--show-log command).
- Trusted users ('trusted_users' regd.conf option).


